generated_description: bioexato is a laboratory based in turuçu, rio grande do sul, founded on august 4, 2007. the company provides clinical analysis and diagnostic services, including blood, urine, and fecal tests, as well as veterinary and toxicological exams. bioexato emphasizes the use of advanced technology and automated equipment to ensure the reliability and quality of its results. the laboratory also offers preventive vaccines, pre-cancer screenings, and home and business collection services. bioexato collaborates with major national laboratories and serves various health insurance providers and local government entities.
